definitions.definition: Final , ultimate , coming after all others of its kind.
examples: Eyes Wide Shut was the last film to be directed by Stanley Kubrick.

definitions.definition: Most recent , latest , last so far.
examples: The last time I saw him, he was married.
I have received your note dated the 17th last , and am responding to say that [ … ]

definitions.definition: Farthest of all from a given quality , character , or condition ; most unlikely , or least preferable .
examples: He is the last person to be accused of theft.
The last person I want to meet is Helen.
More rain is the last thing we need right now.

definitions.definition: Being the only one remaining of its class.

examples: Three contestants will win awards, but the last prize is just a book voucher.
